  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Chalet Cairn has a stunning location on the lakeshore in Tignes and is a stylish and comfortable property with six bedrooms. The Tovière gondola and Palafour chiarlift are just three minutes' walk away and the ski shuttle for Val Claret stops outside. Enjoy the hot tub on the terrace or the cosmic sauna, especially when dark with spectacular views over to the illuminated mountain face known as 'The Fingers'. Offered on a chalet catering board basis, you'll enjoy breakfast, afternoon tea and cakes, dinner and wine included with your stay. This chalet sleeps 12-15 people and can be booked for sole occupancy.</p>
<p><strong>Save £100pp when you pre-book your ski pass and lift hire/carriage.</strong></p>]]></listingDescription>
